Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Jonestown massacre
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bvyx
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Dec 1978
Jonestown massacre. 900 cult members die in Rev Jim Jones's jungle camp. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less